README for bat2Script

Descriptions
------------

The source files enclosed in this zip files are:

bat2script
This is a Synergy/DE console application that will convert Workbench build
files from Windows batch files to Unix script files or OpenVMS command files.

dbl2dibol.dbl
dblibr2library.dbl
dblink2link.dbl
These files converts windows command line to OpenVMS command line.

endOfToken.dbl
stringCase.dbl
stringReplace.dbl
These files contain utility functions


